  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2411970/extras/2c8995e391fd3b2e1649b61cb0eb2646.poster.avif?t=1726761567\" width=456 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2411970/extras/2c8995e391fd3b2e1649b61cb0eb2646.webm?t=1726761567\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2411970/extras/2c8995e391fd3b2e1649b61cb0eb2646.mp4?t=1726761567\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Frantic Frank</strong> is late for work!<br>Not only that, those crazy drivers made him lose his papers. <br>Now, he has to get to work fast or face being <strong>FIRED</strong>!<br><br>Don’t fret, since <strong>Frantic Frank </strong>can drive like a fiend.<br>Fly in and out of traffic with ease, flit through<br>lights, and grab your papers  to save your job!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2411970/extras/6770d22948136124c2da01c9fb6e2b57.poster.avif?t=1726761567\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2411970/extras/6770d22948136124c2da01c9fb6e2b57.webm?t=1726761567\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2411970/extras/6770d22948136124c2da01c9fb6e2b57.mp4?t=1726761567\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br>•\t<strong>Arcade perfect controls</strong>: Change lanes instantly, and thrill to tight dodges!<br><br>•\tJudge just the right moment to run the light or slam the brakes!<br><br>•\tEvade <strong>wacky drivers</strong> like Tail Gator, Speed Demon, Slow Poke, Sundae Driver, and more!<br><br>•\tGrab <strong>powerups </strong>to gain the edge like the Chain Mace, the Spike Plow, and the Turbo Gas!<br><br>•\tKeep your eyes peeled for letters and spell <strong>“BUMPY”</strong> for an extra bit of pep!<br><br>•\t<strong>12 unique areas</strong>, each with their own crazy, enemy driver!<br><br>•\tPick up your lost paper work and drive to <strong>3 different endings</strong>!<br><br>•\tNo Quarter: <strong>arcade precision</strong> back from 1983—tough but fair. Perfect game balance!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2411970/extras/cd49b17b6bdd3a8dc7c553c034b98830.poster.avif?t=1726761567\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2411970/extras/cd49b17b6bdd3a8dc7c553c034b98830.webm?t=1726761567\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>•\tPoints are life: Gain more points to gain extra lives and extend your run!<br><br>•\tSuper Scoring: Get points for passing drivers, but gain up to x5 points for passing fast!<br><br>•\t<strong>Secret Points:</strong> Discover subtle points by cutting drivers off both coming and going!<br><br>•\t<strong>Global Leaderboards:</strong> Go for the high score!<br><br>•\tMAME ready: Controls already mapped, <strong>drop it into your arcade cabinet tonight</strong>!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2411970/extras/486587dbc94ca9f6ca7375ea7c084f6a.poster.avif?t=1726761567\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2411970/extras/486587dbc94ca9f6ca7375ea7c084f6a.webm?t=1726761567\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2411970/extras/486587dbc94ca9f6ca7375ea7c084f6a.mp4?t=1726761567\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CHECK OUT MOMMY'S BEST GAMES NEXT RELEASE</h2>",
